text: Magnus Westman (born 9 August 1966) is a Swedish ski jumper. He competed at the 1992 Winter Olympics and the 1994 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Sweden Category:Ski jumpers at the 1992 Winter Olympics Category:Ski jumpers at the 1994 Winter Olympics Category:People from Örnsköldsvik Municipality
